== ICC Learning Project ==

This project has as goals:
* Learning how to use Git to work in a distibuted workflow
* Learning the base system of ScriptedAI (Base-class for SD2 Creature scripts)
* Learning the base system of how SD2 handles instance scripts
* Learning how to structure research about bosses, to get solid scripts for them
* Learning how to interact with the MaNGOS project and database projects to do things _right_
